{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alliance Peacefighter is a linear, story-driven space sim in the style of the 90s classics. As a newly qualified Alliance pilot, you find yourself caught up in a plot to break the fragile peace between two galactic super powers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538210/extras/alliance_peacefighter_screen_10.jpg?t=1740412021\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of the Alliance's most advanced starfighter in a thrilling story-driven campaign.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced first-person combat, with full control over your ship's power and shield distribution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear, diegetic UI provides critical information at a glance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight alongside an elite squad of quirky alien teammates. Then relax in the ship's bar.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Built for both VR and traditional monitors, with full support for motion controllers, HOTAS joysticks, gamepads and mouse/keyboard. The Steam Deck is also fully supported (official verification still pending).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Alliance Peacefighter is a tribute to the golden age of space sims, and a love letter to the people who grew up with them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538210/extras/BOOM.jpg?t=1740412021\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3538210?t=1740412021","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538210/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740412021","capsule_image":"https://share